DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nGood day everyone\,\
 n\nPlease join us for a fantastic **St. Paddy's Dinner and DJ party** as w
 e mix\, mingle\, make new friends and then dance the night away to a fabul
 ous DJ! Playing all the best from the 70s\, 80s\, 90s\, 2000s and your req
 uests too!\n\n\\*Joined by my other social groups too\; so we can anticipa
 te a terrific turn out with lots of friendly peers to enjoy dinner and the
  lively dance floor!\n\n**Date:** Tuesday March 17th\, 2026\n**Location:**
  747 Mt. Pleasant (Smoke Show)\n\n**\\*Meet us inside Smoke Show between 6
 :00 pm and 7:30 pm (arrive later if you have too)**\n\\*If you have to arr
 ive after that\, still let the front door staff know you are with **Steve'
 s group** so they can direct you to us (but kindly do your best to arrive 
 between 6:00 pm and 7:30 pm -Thank you!\n(You will be paying me not the pe
