SUMMARY:Steve Flemming's Love Songs that Stir the Soul (Thursday March 19t
 h) 
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 Please join us **on zoom** for a fun\, relaxing and inspiring evening with
  **Love Songs that Stir the Soul.**\n\nSongs that I have written for well 
 over 36 years.\nYou will love what you hear! :)\nNew songs every week\, in
 cluding some of our favorites!\n\n\\*You are welcome to join us any time a
 fter 8:30 pm (Eastern Time)\n\\*You are also welcome to come on later in t
 he evening as well\n**\\*\\*Attend for free if you like - if it's your fir
 st time attending :)**\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Fle
 mming\n(Songwriter/Producer/Host)\n\nEvent Details:\n**Steve Flemming's Lo
 ve Songs that Stir the Soul (Thursday\, March 19th)**\n**(on Zoom)**\n\n\\
 *Original Lyrics and Songs by Songwriter and Producer Steve Flemming\n\n\\
 *Story songs\, love songs\, spiritual songs\, songs about nature\, our cul
 ture\, our past\, our future\, relationships and our lives\n\nI'll be play
 ing a mix of songs using a fusion of mixed genres like\, **Folk\, Traditio
 nal Folk\, Country\, Blue Grass\, Singer Song Writer\, Soft Rock\, Easy Li
 stening\, Classic Rock\, R & B\, Gospel\, Pop\, Adult Contemporary\, Indie
  Rock/Po**p and many others genres too. So please sit back and get ready t
 o have an amazing auditory experience in the comforts of your own home :)\
 n\n\\*You can come on and off at any time during the night- starting at 8:
 30 pm\n\n**About Steve Flemming:**\nHighly influenced by the great singer 
 songwriters of the 50s\, 60s\, 70s\, 80s and 90s. I have been writing my o
 wn songs since 1990. Songs about life\, love\, loss\, hope\, faith\, joy\,
  romance\, memories\, spirituality and heartbreak. Songs that are universa
 l\, heartfelt and often relevant to the lives of many others.\n\n\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Event Fee:**\n\n**Pay What You Can: (P.W.Y.C)**\nYou ca
 n kindly send through e transfer or pay pal to:\n**steveflemming11@gmail.c
 om**\n\n-Anything you can contribute is greatly appreciated to help suppor
 t this meaningful musical endeavor and song loving community\n\n\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Zoom 
 link:**\n\nhttps://us04web.zoom.us/j/495043928\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Testimonials from Past Event
 s:**\nYour songs are wonder-full\, speak to emotions\, experiences and mom
 ents we've all felt and lived. S. B.\nSteve Flemming is an amazing songwri
 ter whose lyrics stir the soul. He transforms everyday thoughts and life i
 nto beautiful poetry and magical tunes. Amazing stuff yet again Steve. - L
 .L.\nSteve\, thank you for a night of heartfelt\, exhilarating\, and inspi
 ring music.\nV.R.\nThanks for having me my friend. I love your words\, the
 y calm me and energize me at the same time I'll look forward to your next 
 invite\nM.Z.\nThese great songs definitely helped me to decompress after a
  long day. Keep up the song writing Steve\, these are great! - S.S.\nThank
  you so much for a relaxing evening and sharing your inspiring music Steve
 ! I am excited to hear more and I hope you do this again!! - C.B\nLovely s
 ongs and a great vibe with wonderful people. I couldn’t have asked for a
  better way to close my day. Huge thanks Steve\, for inviting me! I truly 
 enjoyed every moment! - N.A.\nThe lyrics are amazing. From the heart...\nT
 hanks Steve for the amazing tunes. I'm truly blown away. Very glad I joine
 d.\n\\- E\\.E\\.\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
