SUMMARY:Friday Brunch! (What is Love?) (with Steve and MJ) (on Zoom) 
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 Please join us for an insightful and interactive event as we dive deeper i
 nto understanding the real meaning and demonstration of Love. within in ro
 mantic\, intimate and committed relationships.\n\nWe all bring years of kn
 owledge\, wisdom\, stories and even questions' so together we can support\
 , inspire and share our views on love.\n\nThis will be a well organized\, 
 interactive and a much needed conversation\; so please join us if you can.
 \n\n\\*I will be hosting this event with a friend (MJ) who is also quite p
 assionate and well spoken on the topic of what is Love?\n\nThanks again ev
 eryone!\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host)\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
